    "全程走虚拟网卡（TUN），整机流量自动经隧道转发，无需配置系统代理。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All traffic goes through a virtual network interface (TUN) and is forwarded via the tunnel automatically — no system proxy configuration needed."
          }
